Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.76,0:14:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We have secured the finest coach to teach you, \Nin the form of Dekanishiki. {no clue what is deka in the beginning, TLC; maybe he means "we hired and commanded a private detective (deka) to eye out/commission/hire an exclusive/emergency/special/personal sumo coach" but why'd harako zaibatsu need some private deka for that?; another suggestion is that deka may be some sumo association or something like that, judging by the fact they commanded it to summon a coach; most likely it's teka - "subordinate; underling; henchman; minion" but it still doesn't add up: why'd he ask underlings for it, he could easily do that himself} {14:10: I'm hearing デカニシキ的に専属コーチを偉大致しましたが\NI want to say デカニシキ is the name of the sumo theacher they hired.\NThe line can be TL'ed loosely as "We have secured the finest coach to teach you, in the form of Dekanishiki" - Au}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.60,0:14:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's not waste a minute more. {/let's start the practice without delay}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.14,0:14:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Look closely, Iyona-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one mighty river! Falling into it would mean \Ngetting carried away by the stream and a certain death! {to be washed away; to be carried}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.96,0:14:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Canada is not fooling around!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, for your next training, I need you to enter that river \Nand walk it upward through rapids. Could you do that for me? {"walk against the stream until upper stream; upper course; upper reaches" - later it's revealed they mean up the waterfall}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.09,0:14:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.30,0:14:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Now that's what I call special training!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.32,0:14:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If your legs learn to withstand a stream that mighty, \Nyou'll become immovable on the ring! {/in a flow that great, without yielding/giving an inch, if you train your legs and loins, you'll be invincible}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.81,0:15:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, please be reasonable! \NI'll be dead long before that becomes true! {/don't say mucha}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.59,0:15:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Inflatable Muscles?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.08,0:15:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Heavenly... Ah... Sister Ria's breath \Nis spreading through my whole body. {/filling (guess) me now} {maybe go for something more bold and comedic, like "... is blowing me inside out"}
