Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister Ria, why did you inflate me this much? {/what is this look - I think he means "I'm fat and not muscled"}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.27,0:15:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That was not the Inflatable Muscles-kun, \Nbut Infattable Bulge-kun instead. {/chubby/puffed up/plumpy excess flesh; surplus fat; flab-kun}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It suits you greatly, Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.35,0:15:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.73,0:15:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This ushers in the high tide of the special training! {/is in full swing}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.71,0:16:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,When your body is made chubby with Infattable Bulge-kun, \Nthe small injuries should not bother you. {/made round/curled up ..., (with just a) small amount; a bit; only a little(​with neg. sentence), cannot hurt - unsure whether she means "you won't be hurt more than superficially" or "small injuries won't hurt you" or smt else}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.84,0:16:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm a bit unsightly this way. Sister Ria, \Nhow about you blow me with Inflatable Muscles-kun instead? {/a bit unattractive; ugly; unstylish; uncool}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.22,0:16:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough dilly-dallying! \NGet in the damn water! {/enough going on and on (about inconsequential things); talking nonsense​, hurry up and go}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.09,0:16:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{oh hey, fuzakeru-chan}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.65,0:16:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru! Take a grip of your lower body \Nand keep it close to the ground, like during sumo line-drawing! {/keeping your lower back; waist; hips; lumbar region down/low/close to ground, imitate what they do during preliminary warm-up ritual; toeing the mark​(Sumo)}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.66,0:16:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this pose!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.41,0:16:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Draw the line now! {no clue what is this senka/senga; might TLC but I think "line drawing" is correct here}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.44,0:16:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, this stance is the key! {/in this shape} \NI can withstand the stream! {/I'm not getting borrowed/carried away}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.42,0:16:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! Now start moving upstream \Nwith your feet on the ground! {/next start moving one's legs forward without letting one's feet leave the ground(​Sumo) forward/ahead of you}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.96,0:16:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Feet on the ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But first, keep both your arms \Npinned down to the body. {not really sure first word is mazu} {/squeeze both hands to the armpits}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.89,0:16:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, start moving forward, \Nsliding your feet against the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.68,0:17:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see! By raising the leg, you disturb your balance, \Nthen the stream can easily carry you off! {/getting washed away}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.27,0:17:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Also think of the water trying to carry you off \Nas your opponent. {/... that you're fighting}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.85,0:17:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,To be able to advance, \Nyou need to push it aside first! {not sure where " in one go; in one gulp; in one breath; without stopping; without pausing; without a rest; in one sitting; at a stretch" belongs here, maybe like "push him and then move forward this instant"}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.73,0:17:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,To battle! To battle! {this tl is not as good in this situation, but "come at me" would be even worse so w/e}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.90,0:17:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep trying, Honmaru! {unsure what exactly this is, most likely smt along the lines of "keep trying/repeat until succeed"}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.10,0:17:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,To battle! To battle! To battle! To battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.07,0:17:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, Jabao! Come, Harako! {okay, here come at me would've worked better since he is making a direct address with it now as "I'm talking to jabao and harako too"}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.74,0:17:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,To battle! To battle! To battle! To battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.05,0:17:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it all! Never again am I giving Iyona-chan \Na reason to think of me as a Li'l Pants Wetter! {/nobody ever again calls me Li'l Pants Wetter in front of .../says I'm ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.52,0:17:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,To battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.49,0:17:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! That's the spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.35,0:17:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, great progress!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,To bat—
