Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.24,0:18:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Start anew! {/once again}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.66,0:18:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Shucks! To battle! To battle! To battle. To battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.25,0:18:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru! Your waist is not low enough \Nand your center of gravity is too high!  {/lower you center of gravity by keeping your hips lower}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.34,0:18:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And mind your hips when moving forward! {/Then advance with/to your hips/waist - really unsure what he means by that}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it all! To battle! To battle! To battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.60,0:18:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Lower your hips more!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.10,0:18:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,To battle! To battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.02,0:18:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the way! Stay collected! {/don't relax}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.09,0:18:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,To battle! To battle. To...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.32,0:18:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad! This special training is still too much for me! {after all}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.12,0:18:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's return to Japan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.52,0:18:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so good about this special training \Nin the great wilderness?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.68,0:18:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fed up with trees, mountains and people - \Neveryone is getting on my nerves! {/I hate everything}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.65,0:18:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And this stupid body -
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.51,0:19:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the most deplorable! {/I have most of all - unsure if he means inflated body or his usual body}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.81,0:19:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru is playing in the wateru-ru-ru with us, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.94,0:19:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk! Where I'm facing the ordeal of special training, \Nhe's just splashing around! {/even though I'm suffering the ... here, you're just playing in the water?}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So cold and so refreshing! {/it's cold and it feels good}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.34,0:19:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Niruru, let's have a race! {/let's see the fastest to the cliff!} {/Let's have a competition}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.83,0:19:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good to be always carefree. \NLike those two. I swear! {unsure if it's futari ha and not taru ha}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.75,0:19:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.68,0:19:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But how...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it possible for Taru \Nto just swim through the rapid upwards so playfully? {/how taru and co are able to climb against the swift current; rapids cliff/slope so lightly and smoothly} {hope it's suisui, was "yasuyasu" in manga; kyuuryuu wo saka noborerunda}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.55,0:19:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru! Canadian Creek-chan is friend, too! {カナダの水っちゃん - basically, any water I think}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.16,0:19:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, Taruruuto! {/glad you came}\NLet's play together!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.62,0:20:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And look out, I can go pretty high!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.76,0:20:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Alley-hop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.84,0:20:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. It just dawned upon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.33,0:20:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn right, Honmaru! \NThis is something your body had already learned long ago! {oboeta koto}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.92,0:20:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Using your whole body \Nto read the flow of nature, not oppose it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.38,0:20:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing through it with your heart! {/it's something you see ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.65,0:20:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I had completely forgotten…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.15,0:20:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru doesn't have to cast a spell on it \Nfor the water to be alive. {/water has a heart too}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The trees, the soil, and the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.39,0:20:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything around me is alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.37,0:20:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.17,0:21:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.09,0:21:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,To battle! To battle! To battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.14,0:21:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.60,0:21:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, you came to see the water's alive! {/realized the heart of water}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.15,0:21:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly! Opposing the stream gets you nowhere! \NMerging with the stream is the way to go! {/instead of going against the flow, I should find the path inside the flow}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.06,0:21:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Merging! {/the road/path}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.70,0:21:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.74,0:21:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,To battle! To battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.23,0:21:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep going, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.31,0:21:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking good! Keep this up, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.00,0:21:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,To battle! To battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.30,0:21:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If you merge into it, \Nthe nature and your body work in perfect harmony! {/the nature that is alive becomes one with your own body}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.50,0:21:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, no wildest rapid... {gekiryuu is "raging stream; rapids" and kyuuryuu is "swift current; rapids" and I dunno how to reflect that difference in english}
